PrecisAmendment to SCHEDULE I.1 to the Financial Administration Act which adds the OFFICE OF THE COMMUNICATIONS SECURITY ESTABLISHMENT COMMISSIONER to the list of Divisions or Branches of the Public Service of Canada and names the Minister of NATIONAL DEFENCE as the "appropriate Minister".

precis:
Amendment to SCHEDULE I.1 to the Financial Administration Act which adds
the OFFICE OF THE COMMUNICATIONS SECURITY ESTABLISHMENT COMMISSIONER to
the list of Divisions or Branches of the Public Service of Canada and
names the Minister of NATIONAL DEFENCE as the "appropriate Minister".
